    "description": "Poker Ball combines the rules of poker with matching games for an all new puzzle experience!  This is a fast paced game, using just Tens, Jacks, Queens, Kings, and Aces.  Fun for any fan of cards, but also fun for the kids to enjoy too!<br><br><br><strong>MULTIPLE LANGUAGE SUPPORT!</strong><br>English, हिन्दी, Français, Deutsche, 한국어, 简体中文, Español, Português, 日本語, Melayu<br><br><br><strong>LEVEL MODE</strong><br>Play through the levels, with each level being slightly more challenging than the last.  Clear the PokerBalls by matching Straights, Flushes, Full Houses, Four of a Kinds, or score big with a Royal Flush.<br>As the game progresses, you'll have more PokerBalls to clear, and the pieces start to drop faster and faster.  See how high you can score, and compare with your friends and family!<br><br><br><strong>ARCADE MODE</strong><br>Poker Balls will be placed on the screen as you play, and the game gets faster as you go!<br><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br>* Replay past levels - see your scores from previous levels, and replay them to try to beat your last score<br>* Volume control - Set the volume for music and sound effects however you like<br>* Simple, and all original, piano tunes<br>* Pause - Pause the game at any time to plan your next move",
